  "notes": "SBSeg 2013 (XIII), Manaus/AM, hosted by IComp/UFAM. Main-track Program Committee ('Comitê de Programa') extracted from the original site sbseg2013.icomp.ufam.edu.br via the Wayback Machine (snapshot 2013-09-14); the GitHub clone https://sbseg-sbc.github.io/sbseg2013/ only lists coordinators, not full PC members. 47 PC members listed (alphabetical by first name). Chairs ('Coordenação do Comitê de Programa', from the Chamada de Trabalhos page) are Michel Abdalla and Raul Ceretta Nunes, who also appear in the members list. Jorge Nakahara Junior had no affiliation shown on the source page. The recurring footer name 'Marcel Cunha' (site developer credit) is not a committee member and was excluded."
